==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Bunion
<hw>Bun"ion</hw> }</mhw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. Prov. E. <ets>bunny</ets> a small swelling, fr.
OF. <ets>bugne</ets>, It. <ets>bugna</ets>, <ets>bugnone</ets>. See
<er>Bun</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>An enlargement and
inflammation of a small membranous sac (one of the <xex>burs⟦ae⟧
muscos⟦ae⟧</xex>), usually occurring on the first joint of the great
toe.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

